title: Ep259 F*cked Up Firsts
description:
This week, the gals all share tales of breakthrough crimes. Topics include a mid-air homicide, a safe harbor for insurrectionists, and the mysterious disappearance of a national hero. Mix up a Canadian cocktail, rethink those flying lessons, and tune in for F*cked Up Firsts.
